  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/c50cbe98437eb432357bcdacda997a2d.avif?t=1732984209\" width=520 height=160 /></span><br><br>4 New Crabs, 4 New Minigames, 4 New Achievements!<br><strong>And Brand New Island!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/66c1d3258956d0031c3b6acf959a25aa.poster.avif?t=1732984209\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/66c1d3258956d0031c3b6acf959a25aa.webm?t=1732984209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/66c1d3258956d0031c3b6acf959a25aa.mp4?t=1732984209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gray, Red, Green and Blue Crabs</strong> appeared on a <strong>Brand New Island</strong>!<br>Play their <strong>Minigames</strong> to get <strong>4 New Achievements</strong> and to compete with other players to see who has the best score!<br><br>You can find Crab Island on the top right corner of your screen on your Main Island Frame.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/1d0540489b10caa4696c8571548efe28.avif?t=1732984209\" width=520 height=160 /></span><br><br>\"<strong>Grow a Carrot</strong>\" Is a <strong>Point and Click</strong> style Game, where you are about to find yourself on an <strong>Island full of Bunnies</strong>!<br>There are different ways to obtain Carrots in this fascinating world, Beginning with <strong>planting seeds in your plots</strong> and ending with going to another <strong>universe</strong> to find the mysterious <strong>Golden Carrot</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/f98d03cacacb614298b2f50c16db0f9f.poster.avif?t=1732984209\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/f98d03cacacb614298b2f50c16db0f9f.webm?t=1732984209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/f98d03cacacb614298b2f50c16db0f9f.mp4?t=1732984209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Meet all the <strong>Bunnies</strong> in the <strong>Village</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/108a638e9187a4522b4bae42bbe41399.apng?t=1732984209\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/108a638e9187a4522b4bae42bbe41399.poster.avif?t=1732984209\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=120 /></picture></span><br><br>Get all the <strong>Achievements</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/5988a51d17aef29eebec381e991c2791.poster.avif?t=1732984209\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/5988a51d17aef29eebec381e991c2791.webm?t=1732984209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/5988a51d17aef29eebec381e991c2791.mp4?t=1732984209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect all the <strong>Tokens</strong> as <strong>Steam Items</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/b41243f5d860789f75058315e1217aa3.avif?t=1732984209\" width=415 height=325 /></span><br><br><strong>While playin</strong>g \"<strong>Grow a Carrot</strong>\", <strong>every hour</strong> you will get a <strong>random token</strong>!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/3cf8c2e7bf3ffee219539f9e5aea83bd.webp?t=1732984209\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794860/extras/3cf8c2e7bf3ffee219539f9e5aea83bd.poster.avif?t=1732984209\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=320 /></picture></span><br><br>I created \"<strong>Grow a Carrot</strong>\" to <strong>learn</strong> few things about developing a game, and it became <strong>my playground, my sandbox</strong>.<br>You will clearly see how strange ideas I can have in mind. <br><br><strong>Have fun, and remember to always Grow a Carrot!</strong><br><br><br><br>\"Grow a Carrot\" powered by Clickteam Fusion 2.5",
